'''印度－英国关系'''，是指[[印度共和國|印度共和國]]和[[大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合王國|大不列顛及北愛爾蘭聯合王國]]之間的雙邊關係。印度在英国[[倫敦|倫敦]]設有高級專員公署，亦在[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]和[[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]設有總領事館<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hcilondon.in/contactus.php |title=High Commission of India in the UK |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2013-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130115052916/http://hcilondon.in/contactus.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。英國在[[新德里|新德里]]設高級專員公署，又在五個印度城市（即[[孟買|孟買]]、[[欽奈|欽奈]]、[[班加羅爾|班加羅爾]]、[[海得拉巴_(印度)|海得拉巴]]和[[加爾各答|加爾各答]]）設有副高級專員公署<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ukinindia.fco.gov.uk/en/about-us/other-locations/ |title=British embassy in India |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2013-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130316085055/http://ukinindia.fco.gov.uk/en/about-us/other-locations |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。這兩個國家都是[[英聯邦|英聯邦]]的正式成員。自1947年，兩國關係一直友好。[[英国首相|英国首相]][[戴維·卡梅倫|戴維·卡梅倫]]在2010年曾描述印度和英国的關係是“新興的特殊關係”<ref name=culture1>{{cite news |title=Does India want a 'special relationship' with UK? |first=Chris |last=Morris |authorlink=Chris Morris (journalist) |newspaper=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=27 July 2010 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-south-asia-10782552 |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2016-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205044437/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-south-asia-10782552 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=culture2>{{cite news |title=Ministers to build a new 'special relationship' with India |first=Dean |last=Nelson |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=7 July 2010 |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/politics/conservative/7877719/Ministers-to-build-a-new-special-relationship-with-India.html |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2011-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110207103129/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/politics/conservative/7877719/Ministers-to-build-a-new-special-relationship-with-India.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

印度和英國主要是通過多邊合作組織（如[[英聯邦|英聯邦]]、[[世界貿易組織|世界貿易組織]]、[[亞洲開發銀行|亞洲開發銀行]]等）在政治上合作。歷史上有三名[[印度總統|印度總統]]曾國事訪問英國，包括[[薩瓦帕利·拉達克里希南|薩瓦帕利·拉達克里希南]]、[[拉馬斯瓦米·文卡塔拉曼|拉馬斯瓦米·文卡塔拉曼]]及[[普拉蒂巴·帕蒂爾|普拉蒂巴·帕蒂爾]]<ref name="statevisitstouk">{{cite web |title=Ceremonies: State visits |url=http://www.royal.gov.uk/output/Page4935.asp |publisher=Official web site of the British Monarchy |accessdate=2008-11-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081106153300/http://www.royal.gov.uk/output/Page4935.asp |archivedate=2008-11-06 }}</ref>； 

[[英國女王|英國女王]][[伊麗莎白二世|伊麗莎白二世]]曾在1963年11月、1990年4月和1997年10月國事訪問印度<ref>{{cite web |title=OUTWARD STATE VISITS MADE BY THE QUEEN SINCE 1952 |url=http://www.royal.gov.uk/output/page4869.asp |publisher=Official web site of the British Monarchy |accessdate=2008-11-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081021220621/http://www.royal.gov.uk/output/Page4869.asp |archivedate=2008-10-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title= OUTWARD STATE VISITS MADE BY THE QUEEN SINCE 1952|url= http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchUK/RoyalVisits/Commonwealthvisitssince1952.aspx|publisher= Official web site of the British Monarchy|accessdate= 2011-05-24|archive-date= 2015-04-12|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150412031035/http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchUK/RoyalVisits/Commonwealthvisitssince1952.aspx|dead-url= no}}</ref>。法國外交家{{link-en|马克福|Marc Fonbaustier}}曾指印度是英國在[[亞洲|亞洲]]政治和戰略的關鍵，兩國亦有著共同的價值觀<ref>Eric Deville, [http://digitaljournal.com/article/343948 Op-Ed: Cameron’s visit to India — Pounds, rupees and democracy] {{Wayback|url=http://digitaljournal.com/article/343948 |date=20150705183300 }}, ''Digital Journal'', 20 February 2013</ref>。

